          <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line text-white text-xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl tracking-tight mb-3">Phoenix Real Estate Strength</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Central Phoenix (602) remains one of the most desirable and active housing markets in the metro. Owning this name gives you a permanent advantage.</p>
