            <h2 class="text-[2.75rem] leading-[1.1] font-bold tracking-tighter">Central Phoenix remains one of the most active and desirable housing markets in the metro.</h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600">The 602 encompasses iconic central Phoenix neighborhoods &mdash; Arcadia, Camelback, Biltmore, and surrounding areas &mdash; where demand for homes, real estate expertise, and trusted local services stays consistently strong.</p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-x-3 text-sm">
              <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl text-center">
                <div class="font-mono text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Strong</div>
                <div class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 tracking-wider">Buyer &amp; Seller Demand</div>
              </div>
              <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl text-center">
                <div class="font-mono text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Premium</div>
