              <div class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tighter">Significant</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">&ldquo;Casa&rdquo; resonates powerfully with Arizona&rsquo;s large and growing Spanish-speaking market &mdash; a clear competitive edge.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-slate-500 px-1">Phoenix metro housing market remains dynamic. Central Phoenix (602) neighborhoods like Arcadia and Camelback continue to command strong interest due to location, schools, and lifestyle amenities.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Domain Value -->
  <section id="value" class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
